{"tid":1241134,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2018-2019年度 香港警務處有206億budget維穩啊！！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-18T15:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T23:59:36.000Z","uid":49813,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14a497afeb6c7c10d844cf83911bf9715bce51ff","tid":1241134,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/pdf/chead122.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fpdf%2Fchead122.pdf&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8HljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=898426a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/pdf/chead122.pdf</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">D錢用來做咩既呢</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n香港警務處(警隊)<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">維持治安</span></strong></span>，主要是透過調派軍裝人員<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到各處巡邏，清楚展示充足警力及其高度靈活調動性</span></span></strong>。警隊藉着不斷監察罪案趨勢、仔細部署公眾活動安排和應用經改良的指揮及<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">控制電腦系統</span></span></strong>，有成效及有效率地調配警隊資源<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得要洗咁多錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好抵啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映<br />\n基於近日警察的英勇行為 應該檢討一下警察薪津福利<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1232607/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1232607/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"834c4720027da9095e5972d63f0c1561591a5563","tid":1241134,"uid":49813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:02:49.000Z","msg":"講錯係2019-2020年度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d968769a3ff6a9ac7d0f7dc6985106432247dfa1","tid":1241134,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b2f5caa0284b52fab4c9023b7071b042e655b7","tid":1241134,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f47e848591689b4773b6ea3df0265d816ef82ebf","tid":1241134,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8c7905e1d695f118b91014f6cf2e254474aba3","tid":1241134,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178c8d0cff6230c6a7bfea61a89b4ac4cafe8cec","tid":1241134,"uid":252311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bfadc50bfea3ea8ac339df9b2cf29a739cc193","tid":1241134,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43efb5b97711962fb7e0ca2c05d2b71a43dae074","tid":1241134,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2